{"tid":448304,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"如果2月去札幌 有咩節目同預幾多好？","createTime":"2017-10-26T05:43:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T17:16:28.000Z","uid":140630,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"adbe3a760babb50608f5accb9f059f095fc5875b","tid":448304,"uid":140630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T05:43:53.000Z","msg":"小弟同朋友兩個人打算2月去札幌<br />\n聽聞個到有雪祭玩<br />\n如果預1萬多小小夠唔夠？<br />\n求建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daab8a93222a4e26fb5bc5380af7a47a1bb9b675","tid":448304,"uid":44814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T05:46:01.000Z","msg":"你去幾多日？<br />\n想食好住好 普通 慳住用？<br />\n基本想去邊度玩？<br />\n屌你乜都唔講攤大隻手"},{"pid":"7b49c4c4f1e4b6c1315411b361a472eeab975c3c","tid":448304,"uid":83094,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T05:47:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a86705416605dc1a4fdc368bab0edbae2cf85d0d","tid":448304,"uid":30368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:02:36.000Z","msg":"我12月去plan哂行程喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e4646c1142f91afce8ca85bc19c01e8dd24653","tid":448304,"uid":140630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:16:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你去幾多日？<br />\n想食好住好 普通 慳住用？<br />\n基本想去邊度玩？<br />\n屌你乜都唔講攤大隻手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我第一次係旅行台post文 唔係好識 sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 小弟應該去5至6日 普普通通咁玩<br />\n應該係札幌 小樽呢d位玩<br />\n第一次去日本 唔係好熟路"},{"pid":"3ce62635db53d219482b76a43461d4c8ddc3ecb7","tid":448304,"uid":142314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:18:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你去幾多日？<br />\n想食好住好 普通 慳住用？<br />\n基本想去邊度玩？<br />\n屌你乜都唔講攤大隻手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我第一次係旅行台post文 唔係好識 sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 小弟應該去5至6日 普普通通咁玩<br />\n應該係札幌 小樽呢d位玩<br />\n第一次去日本 唔係好熟路</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n6日係曬星野 <br />\n完"},{"pid":"df49c0e110e27c024672e219ebe46e0d59dcf03a","tid":448304,"uid":38440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:20:31.000Z","msg":"全部住函館 再去札幌小樽玩 咁會好啲"},{"pid":"514e1fc75eb2d6d09557ab4cd3602b8b898bdbae","tid":448304,"uid":111013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:21:44.000Z","msg":"兩個人一萬定一個人？"},{"pid":"ad3c3f563148198c0befea8d56371d9e7e7cef5f","tid":448304,"uid":119807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:53:58.000Z","msg":"認真答你，一萬只係夠買機票同酒店，雪祭時期機票同酒店都貴勁多，價錢大約係平時二到三倍，岩岩就咁睇一睇，機票大約五千，酒店大部份都要千幾蚊一晚<br />\n<br />\n雪祭要早最小大半年就開始Plan先可以搵到平機票同酒店，雪祭值得去，但睇你肯唔肯比多小小錢"},{"pid":"8cf32297a281a995852a8c8d94941aa1201b2833","tid":448304,"uid":118455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:41:13.000Z","msg":"雪祭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f3f5c083159b722cba9021972b1a72fcc448b11","tid":448304,"uid":77704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:14:09.000Z","msg":"岩岩去完10日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n洗左20萬&yen; 仲未計卡數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"846c21da433ec83f079be93ff698bac7af1b3941","tid":448304,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:17:32.000Z","msg":"而家plan雪祭太遲吧，睇你俾得起幾多錢"},{"pid":"90d342dfeaeca79d442a17ebb1b22fb0f18e312f","tid":448304,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T11:12:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家plan雪祭太遲吧，睇你俾得起幾多錢</blockquote><br />\n唔遲，伸多幾個月手都仲得。"},{"pid":"1b3ca4498f5c457dd3aa3db867719724058d68f4","tid":448304,"uid":149613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T11:22:31.000Z","msg":"一萬多少少去大阪東京就夠，去札幌預兩萬一個人啦"},{"pid":"007de952a802fc40c80231dfe4b0db79c265aa